title: PE的seed收集贴 8.8更新(持续更新)
txt_content:
本帖最后由 719823597 于 2012-8-8 22:01 编辑 

先声明 此贴专门收集PE的seed  别在PC的试了无效后来问我为什么

黑体字是seed  蓝色字是发布者给的描述与我的翻译


998

Big floating islands, waterfalls, cliffs, and a huge mob den!
(大浮岛 瀑布 悬崖 和巨大地牢= =？)


foxyy
-56729291D

Best seed ever                                                                                
(最好的seed......我没试过= =)


 nicessssshouse

It has an amazing mountain system with caves
(有一座令人惊奇的山和一些洞穴)


2477291

There are two lavafalls near each other, and a sand mountain
(有两个很靠近的岩浆瀑布，还有一座沙子山)


Reventon21

Tall mountains, overhangs, and caves!
(高山，悬岩和洞穴)


40

EPIC cliffs, waterfall, and twisted mountain
(史诗般的悬崖，瀑布和古怪的山)


Horrid Seed

Freakishly tall, amazing mountains, deep valleys, a waterfall & a lavafall, floating islands, bridges connecting mountains, deep caves, etc.
(高得奇怪的山，深谷，水瀑布和岩浆瀑布，浮岛，山之间有桥，很深的洞穴等等)


infinity

you spawn near the most epic cave ever this is a must try seed                                                                                
(你出生点的附近有许多史诗般的洞穴，这是一个必须一试的seed)


nyan

lava falls and a huge cave
(岩浆瀑布和巨大洞穴)


nike 

lots of ice
(许多雪)


z 

lots of lava
(许多岩浆)


FUUUUUUUUUU 

cool hills
(很酷的山)
